nodes.title: 控制画面风格
widgets_values:
FluxGuidance节点 控制风格
禁用FluxGuidance节点，自动回到默认3.5数值

值越低，图像越有创意和抽象，使用 1.2 到 2 之间，绘画风格最佳
1.9：真实感
任何高于 4 的值都会看起来不正常

3.5：效果最佳(默认值)1：绘画风格灰暗破旧
1.4：灰暗破旧｜1.9：真实感｜2.8：简洁｜11：更多细节节
可在0～100之间自行测试

通过控制FluxGuidance不同数值，给不同微调方案吧，
但保持95%基本相似基础，就是图像保持不变，微调的一种方法

Realistic style，
Title: Display the title "The Crazy Adventure of the Ninja Chicken" in bold and playful text at the top or center of the poster.
Main Character: Depict a dynamic and charismatic ninja chicken in a heroic pose, wearing a traditional ninja outfit with a mask, while still showing chicken features like feathers and a beak.
Background: Include a colorful and exciting backdrop with elements like a mystical forest, a bustling city, and an ancient temple to hint at various adventures. Ensure the background is vibrant and engaging.
Supporting Characters: Add a few quirky and fun supporting characters such as a wise old turtle, a mischievous squirrel sidekick, and a villainous fox.
Pixar Branding: Incorporate the Pixar logo at the bottom or top of the poster to establish it as an official Pixar movie.
Tagline: Include a tagline that reads: "An Egg-cellent Adventure Awaits!" prominently on the poster.
Visual Style: Ensure the overall visual style is consistent with Pixar’s signature animation look – bright colors, expressive characters, and a touch of whimsy.

nodes.title: FLUX + 通配符 = 提示词自动智能生成
widgets_values:
FLUX + 通配符 = 提示词自动智能生成
1、”___” 留空 
2、“__promptbuilder/face_”  “__提示生成器/面部_” 控制提示词范围


有些不好表达的词，可以用这符号”___” 留空，让FLUX 自己发挥智能填空内容
要控制提示词生成范围“__promptbuilder/face_” 

例：

提示词：
Photograph of __adjectives__ __promptbuilder/background_beautiful__, featuring a stunning and picturesque scene that evokes magical feelings. In the foreground, a portal opens to a __adjectives__ dimension, with vibrant and otherworldly __common_colors__ colors. A beautiful __nationality__ woman is standing in awe as she observes the scene. Her facial expression conveys __promptbuilder/face_expression__. She is dressed in a __promptbuilder/clothing_dress__, which is elegant and fitting for the fantastical setting. The overall atmosphere captures the enchanting and surreal essence of the scene.

__形容词 __提示生成器/背景__美丽__的照片，照片中的场景令人惊叹，如诗如画，唤起人们神奇的感觉。前景是一个通往__形容词__空间的入口，充满了生机勃勃的__共__色__彩。一位美丽的__国籍__女士站在一旁敬畏地观察着这一场景。她的面部表情表达了__提示生成器/面部_表情__。她身着__提示生成器/服装_裙子__，典雅大方，与奇幻的场景相得益彰。整体氛围抓住了场景迷人和超现实的本质。

1、如当前是（weight_dtype：default）

2、如当前是（weight_dtype：fp8_e4m3fn）
那就改（weight_dtype：default）运行下
再改回（weight_dtype：fp8_e4m3fn）运行，AuraSR即功能起作用
